---
description: FastAPI backend conventions
alwaysApply: true
---

# FastAPI

- Use FastAPI routers under `app/api/routers`.
- Put business logic in `app/services`.
- Put provider integrations in `app/integrations`.
- Keep routers thin.
- Validate request/response models with Pydantic.
- Prefer dependency injection for clients and settings.

# Errors

- Use explicit HTTPException only in API layer.
- Raise domain-specific exceptions in services.
